item.content:encoded: My name is Mihirkumar Vasantbhai Nanda. Right now I am studying in Parul University in Computer Science & Engineering department. I am good at coding in languages like HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript & Python. Also I am developer of WordPress where I like to make websites like blog, e-commerce etc. I like to learn new things and new coding languages! In my hobbies, I just love to do photography in my free time, on the other side I am a professional photographer also. I used to do Wedding photo shoot, Baby Shoot, Prewedding Photo shoot and Cinematography. In editing I use software like Adobe photoshop, Adobe Lightroom, Sony Vegas Pro. And I have very nice grip on all that three software.
